    <h4>Created by Ilya Bokov, Mariko Briggs, Mercedes Chea, and Korey Pecha.</h4>
    <p>Based on the YouTube series, Spicy Ones is a database that stores info about your favorite celebrities and the hot sauces they try on the show.</p>
    <p>Spicy Ones allows fans to easily access unique information about the show, which has become something of a cultural phenomenon. There is no resource out there like Spicy Ones -- we were motivated by the idea of a comprehensive, detailed, and functional databases for hot sauce and pop culture fans alike.</p>
